  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Describe how SI base units are defined.</item>
<item>Describe how derived units are created from base units.</item>
<item>Express quantities given in SI units using metric prefixes.</item>
</list></md:abstract>
